      "title": "Mahinda made another announcement",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa recently spoke on his televsion. As promised on Saturday, I will resign from the presidency today (13). Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardana said that he will send the resignation letter today (13)."
